{"tid":2496315,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"達成協議！孟晚舟自由了","createTime":"2021-04-19T17:34:36.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-19T20:48:54.000Z","uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"91e721ebb46dd3357fd2575810b0ca6493e4b938","tid":2496315,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T17:34:36.000Z","msg":"在滙豐集團、華為及孟晚舟已達成協議情況下，法官頒令，孟晚舟一方可向滙豐索閱有關文件，但部分內容將被遮蓋，相關文件將用於原告在加拿大處理美國提出的引渡聆訊申請。<br />\n<br />\n據報導，今年初，孟晚舟曾透過律師向倫敦法院提出同類的披露申請，但被拒絕。該次申請意在證明，美方指控孟晚舟「隱瞞」華為與香港星通科技關聯，誤導滙豐銀行繼續向華為提供服務的情況不屬實，從而阻止孟晚舟被從加拿大引渡到美國。<br />\n<br />\n報導指出，今年2月，身處加拿大的孟晚舟越洋入稟香港高等法院，要求法庭下令滙豐銀行披露多份有關華為與星通（Skycom）及其母公司內部文件。孟晚舟一方要求法庭向滙豐頒令披露有關涉及華為、星通科技等內部文件紀錄，並批准孟晚舟一方可於孟現時面對的引渡協議程序中，採用該些資料。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BfuTRdYnwZY&amp;ab_channel=%E6%9C%80%E6%96%B0%E6%B6%88%E6%81%AF247\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DBfuTRdYnwZY%26ab_channel%3D%25E6%259C%2580%25E6%2596%25B0%25E6%25B6%2588%25E6%2581%25AF247&d=gloDjMIS9Xq41mamnCswuN7g8jx8mLjpq94TYZylSB8%3D&h=8a0f5a0b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BfuTRdYnwZY&amp;ab_channel=%E6%9C%80%E6%96%B0%E6%B6%88%E6%81%AF247</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qSxiTvUrPYg&amp;t=8s&amp;ab_channel=%E4%BA%86%E4%B8%8D%E8%B5%B7%E6%88%91%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DqSxiTvUrPYg%26t%3D8s%26ab_channel%3D%25E4%25BA%2586%25E4%25B8%258D%25E8%25B5%25B7%25E6%2588%2591%25E7%259A%2584%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259B%25BD&d=gloDjMIS9Xq41mamnCswuN7g8jx8mLjpq94TYZylSB8%3D&h=2f7d0720\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qSxiTvUrPYg&amp;t=8s&amp;ab_channel=%E4%BA%86%E4%B8%8D%E8%B5%B7%E6%88%91%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zV_JOVaONaU&amp;ab_channel=%E5%BF%AB%E7%9C%8B%E8%B5%84%E8%AE%AF%E3%80%90%E7%83%AD%E7%82%B9%E6%96%B0%E9%97%BB%E6%97%B6%E6%94%BF%E7%82%B